text: Thannenkirch is a commune. It is in the Haut-Rhin department of east France. == Geography == Thannenkirch is at an altitude of 468 m in foothill of the Taennchel Massif, 4 km from Ribeauvillé, 11 km from Sélestat and 17 km from Colmar. The village is also close to the Château du Haut-Koenigsbourg. == Related pages == * Communes of the Haut-Rhin department == References == * INSEE commune file ==Other websites== Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin
